      <SectionHeader label="Walk With Me" title="Some paths are meant to be walked together" id="join-title" />
    </div>

    <div class="reveal space-y-6">
      <p>
        On select pilgrimages, a small number of souls will be invited to walk alongside me. To stand on the sacred ground. To participate in ceremony. To feel the earth beneath your feet, not through a screen.
